      • noMeanSqrDistanceTo

        public double noMeanSqrDistanceTo​(RssiFingerprint<S,​R> otherFingerprint)
        Gets squared euclidean distance of signal readings with mean RSSI removed from another fingerprint. Mean RSSI's are taken into account so that bias effects introduced by different device's hardware is partially removed.
        Parameters:
        otherFingerprint - other fingerprint to compare.
        Returns:
        squared euclidean distance of signal readings from another fingerprint with average RSSI's removed.
